General.Name: PermRock Royalty Trust
General.Description: PermRock Royalty Trust operates as a statutory trust in the United States. The company owns interests in the oil and natural gas producing properties. Its underlying properties consist of 22,394 net acres located in the Permian Basin. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Dallas, Texas.
